When I was 14, I underwent ACL Reconstructive surgery on my left knee.
The following are images and documents pertaining to the operation.

<b>Procedure:</b> Left Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction with Posterior Tibialis Allograft.
<b>Orthopaedic Surgeon:</b> Glenn J Huber MD <a href="https://doctor.webmd.com/doctor/glenn-huber-c4f52e00-c30e-49b8-a939-10ac8026d75f-overview?lid=" target="_blank">[profile]</a>
<b>Location:</b> Torrance Little Company of Mary <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Providence+Little+Company+of+Mary+Medical+Center+-+Torrance/@33.8355889,-118.3576693,409a,35y,39.35t/data=!3m1!1e3!4m5!3m4!1s0x80c2b4d216ca6617:0x8729a1c8ce00da8a!8m2!3d33.8386696!4d-118.3573462" target="_blank">[map]</a>
<b>Date:</b> December 22, 2006

