"Both traditional ACL reconstruction surgery and All-Inside ACL reconstruction surgery involve replacing the ACL with a tendon graft. The ruptured ligament is removed and the bone prepared in order for it to accept the new graft which replaces the old ACL." - ACL Reconstruction Treatment Options, Dr. Munjed Al Muderis, 2020. <a href="https://www.almuderis.com.au/knee-surgery/acl-reconstruction/information/acl-reconstruction-treatment-options" target="_blank"><font size="1/2">[source]</font></a>
